productFaciaInfoDetail.description: A fresh take on a footwear classic, these men's Roshe 2 Trainers from Nike redefine simplicity. Paying a nod of respect to the original Roshe One Trainer, the black colourway will get heads turning your way for all the right reasons. Builtwith a stretch foam upper that conforms to your foot for maximum comfort when you're on the move, while the updated sole features three different foam densities for lightweight support and supreme durability. Complete with the iconic Swoosh branding to the sides for one final stamp of quality approval.
